Package org.moeaframework.util.weights

Routines for generating weights for decomposition and reference point methods.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
WeightGenerator Interface for generating a sequence of weights.
 

Class Summary
NormalBoundaryIntersectionGenerator Generates weights using the Normal Boundary Intersection (NBI) method.
RandomGenerator Generates weights randomly.
UniformDesignGenerator Generates weights according to a uniform design of mixtures using the Hammersley low-discrepancy sequence generator.
 

Package org.moeaframework.util.weights Description

Routines for generating weights for decomposition and reference point methods.
